                        </div>
                        <div id="collapseTwelve" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-expanded="false" style="">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>
                                  <strong>1. Purpose</strong> The Employee Welfare Scheme of Technified Labs outlines the various initiatives and benefits offered to employees to enhance their well-being, job satisfaction, and quality of life. This scheme is designed to promote a positive and supportive work environment that fosters employee engagement and loyalty.
