                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  <strong>3. Business Attire</strong> 3.1. Business Professional: Employees are expected to wear business professional attire on designated business days, which includes attire such as formal suits, blouses, dress shirts, ties, and appropriate shoes.
                                </p>
                                <p>3.2. Business Casual: On non-business days, business casual attire is acceptable. This may include slacks, skirts, dress shirts, blouses, sweaters, and appropriate footwear.</p>
                                <p>
